It's a government program.

42:03.054 --> 42:04.556
No. I don't think it is.

42:04.590 --> 42:05.724
What do you mean?

42:05.757 --> 42:08.226
It's not run by the government.

42:08.259 --> 42:09.995
It's a private
military contractor,

42:10.028 --> 42:11.396
Trask Industries.

42:11.429 --> 42:13.932
Trask Industries?

42:13.965 --> 42:16.602
They shut down in '06.

42:16.635 --> 42:17.936
How do you know that?

42:19.638 --> 42:22.073
My father worked there
for 35 years.

42:23.408 --> 42:25.977
Your father worked for Trask?

42:27.946 --> 42:30.481
You think he has something
to do with all this?

42:32.250 --> 42:36.221
(scoffs)
I don't know.

42:36.254 --> 42:39.524
I don't know anything anymore.

42:39.557 --> 42:41.693
It's an exciting time,
Agent Turner.

42:41.727 --> 42:43.729
It's a very exciting time.

42:43.762 --> 42:45.096
We've started with the assets

42:45.130 --> 42:46.431
who can target the
Underground immediately.

42:46.464 --> 42:48.266
You really think
this is gonna work?

42:48.299 --> 42:50.368
I mean, we've been trying
to place spies for years.

42:50.401 --> 42:52.203
Don't think of 'em as spies.

42:52.237 --> 42:54.272
More like weapons.

42:54.305 --> 42:56.574
All if we have to do
is get 'em inside.

42:56.608 --> 42:58.977
The Hounds will take it
from there.

43:25.270 --> 43:27.939
Agent Turner,

43:27.973 --> 43:32.911
we may finally be in a position
to win this war.

