45:00.799 --> 45:04.602
I didn't know what to do
when my powers manifested.

45:04.635 --> 45:07.939
I was scared for myself...
and for my family.

45:09.274 --> 45:12.343
With the tools that I learned
at Empower Academy,

45:12.377 --> 45:15.080
I know that I don't
have to live as a mutant.

45:15.881 --> 45:17.816
I am more than my power.

45:18.950 --> 45:21.953
WOMAN:
Go to EMPOWERACADEMY.COM today

45:21.987 --> 45:24.923
to get your mutant teen
the care they need.

