People have been fighting
for a long time.

45:35.633 --> 45:37.235
And now it's our turn.

45:38.937 --> 45:39.971
Move!

45:41.973 --> 45:44.642
ANNOUNCER:
Critics agree, The Gifted...

45:46.912 --> 45:48.847
It's...

45:50.415 --> 45:51.983
These people need help.

45:52.517 --> 45:54.452
(shouting)

45:54.485 --> 45:58.223
ANNOUNCER:
The Gifted. Mondays on Fox.

